---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Nous joindre · Sherbrooke"
  description="Joindre Express Livraison à Sherbrooke : 873 200-7377, info@expresslivraison.ca. Livraison locale 7 j/7. Sherbrooke, Fleurimont, Rock Forest, Saint-Élie."
  bodyClass="page-contact"
>
  <!-- ========== HERO ========== -->
  <section style="padding:clamp(56px,7vw,96px) 0 32px;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero__meta">
        <span class="pill pill--live"><span class="dot"></span><span data-status>Ouvert · ferme à 21 h</span></span>
        <span class="pill pill--blue">Service 7 J/7</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="h-display" style="font-size:clamp(48px,8vw,112px);margin-top:24px;">
        Touchez le numéro.<br/>Composez. <span class="hero__highlight">Parlez à un humain.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="lead" style="margin-top:24px;">Le téléphone reste la façon la plus rapide. Réponse en quelques sonneries, du lundi au dimanche, pendant nos heures d'ouverture.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ========== BIG PHONE NUMBER ========== -->
  <section style="padding-top:24px;">
    <div class="container">
      <a href="tel:+18732007377" class="big-phone" data-reveal>
        <div class="big-phone__top">
          <div class="mono big-phone__label">Téléphone principal</div>
          <span class="pill pill--live" style="background:rgba(74,255,184,.14);color:#0F8A4D;border-color:rgba(15,138,77,.28);"><span class="dot"></span><span data-status>Ouvert</span></span>
        </div>
        <div class="big-phone__num">
          <span class="big-phone__cc">+1</span>
          <span class="big-phone__chunk">873</span>
          <span class="big-phone__sep">·</span>
          <span class="big-phone__chunk">200</span>
          <span class="big-phone__sep">·</span>
          <span class="big-phone__chunk">7377</span>
        </div>
        <div class="big-phone__hint">
          <div>
            <div class="mono">Touchez pour composer</div>
            <strong>Réponse en quelques sonneries</strong>
          </div>
          <div class="big-phone__arrow" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ========== CONTACT GRID ========== -->
  <section style="background:var(--bg-alt);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head" data-reveal>
        <div>
          <div class="kicker">Autres moyens</div>
          <h2 class="h1" style="margin-top:16px;">Pour ce qui n'est<br/>pas urgent.</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="lead section-head__lead">Pour les questions générales, suggestions, ou collaborations qui peuvent attendre 24 h ouvrables.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="contact-grid">
        <article class="contact-card" data-reveal>
          <div class="contact-card__icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 32 32" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="4" y="8" width="24" height="18" rx="2"/><path d="M4 12l12 8 12-8"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="mono contact-card__label">Courriel</div>
          <a href="mailto:info@expresslivraison.ca" class="contact-card__val">info@<wbr/>expresslivraison<wbr/>.ca</a>
          <p>Questions générales, partenariats, suggestions. Réponse sous 24 h ouvrables.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="contact-card contact-card--primary" data-reveal>
          <div class="contact-card__icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 32 32" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M16 4l-2 6h-8l6 5-2 7 6-4 6 4-2-7 6-5h-8z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="mono contact-card__label">Entreprises</div>
          <a href="/entreprises" class="contact-card__val">Soumission B2B</a>
          <p>Compte d'entreprise, facturation mensuelle, partenariat récurrent. <strong>Voir la page Entreprises</strong> ou demandez par téléphone.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="contact-card" data-reveal>
          <div class="contact-card__icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 32 32" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 6h4a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v18a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-6V14a4 4 0 0 1 4-4z"/><path d="M12 6h-6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v18a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h14v-14a4 4 0 0 0-4-4z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="mono contact-card__label">Facebook</div>
          <a href="https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=61558187126376" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="contact-card__val">/ExpressLivraison ↗</a>
          <p>Actualités, fériés, horaires spéciaux. Messagerie active pendant les heures d'ouverture.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="contact-card contact-card--dark" data-reveal>
          <div class="contact-card__icon" style="background:rgba(74,255,184,.18);color:#4AFFB8;border-color:rgba(74,255,184,.3);">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 32 32" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M28 8c-1 .8-2 1.4-3 1.6.8-.5 1.4-1.2 1.7-2-.8.5-1.6.8-2.5 1A4 4 0 0 0 17 13a11 11 0 0 1-8-4 4 4 0 0 0 1.2 5.3 4 4 0 0 1-1.8-.5 4 4 0 0 0 3.2 4 4 4 0 0 1-1.8.1 4 4 0 0 0 3.7 2.8 8 8 0 0 1-6 1.7 11 11 0 0 0 6 1.7c7.2 0 11.1-6 11.1-11.1v-.5c.8-.6 1.5-1.3 2-2.1z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="mono contact-card__label" style="color:#4AFFB8;">Urgence livraison</div>
          <a href="tel:+18732007377" class="contact-card__val" style="color:#fff;">873 200-7377</a>
          <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);">Pour toute commande en cours ou question pressante : appelez. Toujours plus rapide qu'un courriel.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ========== HOURS + ZONES ========== -->
  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hourszone">
        <div data-reveal>
          <div class="kicker">Heures d'ouverture</div>
          <h2 class="h2" style="margin-top:14px;margin-bottom:24px;">Sept jours,<br/>deux horaires.</h2>
          <div class="hours-card">
            <div class="hours-card__today">
              <span class="pill pill--live"><span class="dot"></span><span data-status>Ouvert</span></span>
            </div>
            <div class="hours-card__row">
              <div>Lundi – Samedi</div>
              <div class="mono">9 h – 21 h</div>
            </div>
            <div class="hours-card__row">
              <div>Dimanche</div>
              <div class="mono">10 h – 17 h</div>
            </div>
            <div class="hours-card__row">
              <div>Jours fériés</div>
              <div class="mono">Variable · appeler</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div data-reveal>
          <div class="kicker">Zones desservies</div>
          <h2 class="h2" style="margin-top:14px;margin-bottom:24px;">Rayon de<br/>0 à 9 km.</h2>
          <ul class="zones-list">
            <li><span class="zd" style="background:var(--blue-600)"></span><strong>Sherbrooke</strong><span class="mono">~2 km · 8 $</span></li>
            <li><span class="zd" style="background:var(--blue-500)"></span><strong>Fleurimont</strong><span class="mono">~5 km · 11 $</span></li>
            <li><span class="zd" style="background:var(--blue-700)"></span><strong>Rock Forest</strong><span class="mono">~7 km · 13 $</span></li>
            <li><span class="zd" style="background:var(--ink)"></span><strong>Saint-Élie-d'Orford</strong><span class="mono">~8 km · 14 $</span></li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mono" style="margin-top:16px;font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);">Hors 9 km ? <a href="tel:+18732007377" style="text-decoration:underline;color:var(--primary);">Appelez</a>, on évalue au cas par cas.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ========== MAP ========== -->
  <section style="background:var(--bg-alt);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head" data-reveal>
        <div>
          <div class="kicker">Carte</div>
          <h2 class="h1" style="margin-top:16px;">Vous êtes ici.<br/>On arrive là.</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="lead section-head__lead">Zone d'opération autour de Sherbrooke. Pas certain si vous êtes dans le rayon ? Un appel et on confirme en 30 secondes.</p>
      </div>
      <figure class="map-figure" data-reveal>
        <svg viewBox="0 0 1200 500" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" role="img" aria-label="Carte de la zone desservie">
          <defs>
            <pattern id="cgrid" x="0" y="0" width="32" height="32" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
              <path d="M32 0H0V32" fill="none" stroke="var(--line)" stroke-width="1"/>
            </pattern>
            <radialGradient id="czg" cx="0.5" cy="0.5" r="0.5">
              <stop offset="0%" stop-color="var(--blue-600)" stop-opacity="0.22"/>
              <stop offset="60%" stop-color="var(--blue-600)" stop-opacity="0.08"/>
              <stop offset="100%" stop-color="var(--blue-600)" stop-opacity="0"/>
            </radialGradient>
          </defs>
          <rect width="1200" height="500" fill="var(--surface)"/>
          <rect width="1200" height="500" fill="url(#cgrid)"/>
          <path d="M0 320 C 200 270, 420 360, 620 310 S 1000 270, 1200 290"
                stroke="var(--blue-300)" stroke-width="20" fill="none" opacity=".3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          <path d="M0 320 C 200 270, 420 360, 620 310 S 1000 270, 1200 290"
                stroke="var(--blue-600)" stroke-width="2" fill="none" opacity=".7"/>
          <text x="1050" y="280" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="12" fill="var(--muted)" letter-spacing="3">RIV. MAGOG</text>

          <circle cx="620" cy="250" r="260" fill="url(#czg)"/>
          <circle cx="620" cy="250" r="260" fill="none" stroke="var(--blue-600)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="6 6" opacity=".4"/>
          <circle cx="620" cy="250" r="180" fill="none" stroke="var(--blue-600)" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4 4" opacity=".3"/>
          <circle cx="620" cy="250" r="100" fill="none" stroke="var(--blue-600)" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4 4" opacity=".3"/>
          <g font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="11" fill="var(--muted)">
            <text x="625" y="156">3 KM · 9 $</text>
            <text x="625" y="76">6 KM · 12 $</text>
            <text x="625" y="-4">9 KM · 15 $</text>
          </g>

          <g font-family="Space Grotesk, sans-serif" font-weight="600">
            <circle cx="620" cy="250" r="16" fill="var(--blue-600)" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="3"/>
            <circle cx="620" cy="250" r="40" fill="none" stroke="var(--blue-600)" stroke-width="1.5" opacity=".4">
              <animate attributeName="r" values="16;80;16" dur="3.4s" repeatCount="indefinite"/>
              <animate attributeName="opacity" values="0.7;0;0.7" dur="3.4s" repeatCount="indefinite"/>
            </circle>
            <text x="650" y="247" font-size="22" fill="var(--ink)">Sherbrooke</text>
            <text x="650" y="265" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="11" fill="var(--muted)" letter-spacing="1">CENTRE · 0 KM · 8 $</text>

            <circle cx="830" cy="160" r="11" fill="var(--blue-500)" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2.5"/>
            <text x="848" y="158" font-size="16" fill="var(--ink)">Fleurimont</text>
            <text x="848" y="174" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="10" fill="var(--muted)" letter-spacing="1">~5 KM · 11 $</text>

            <circle cx="290" cy="340" r="11" fill="var(--blue-700)" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2.5"/>
            <text x="160" y="338" font-size="16" fill="var(--ink)">Rock Forest</text>
            <text x="160" y="354" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="10" fill="var(--muted)" letter-spacing="1">~7 KM · 13 $</text>

            <circle cx="150" cy="220" r="11" fill="var(--ink)" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2.5"/>
            <text x="40" y="208" font-size="16" fill="var(--ink)">Saint-Élie</text>
            <text x="40" y="224" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="10" fill="var(--muted)" letter-spacing="1">~8 KM · 14 $</text>
          </g>

          <g transform="translate(1110 80)">
            <circle r="26" fill="var(--surface)" stroke="var(--line-strong)" stroke-width="1"/>
            <path d="M0 -18 L 6 0 L 0 18 L -6 0 Z" fill="var(--primary)" stroke="var(--ink)" stroke-width="1"/>
            <text x="0" y="-32" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono" font-size="11" font-weight="600" fill="var(--ink)">N</text>
          </g>
        </svg>
      </figure>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ========== FORM (general) ========== -->
  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head" data-reveal>
        <div>
          <div class="kicker">Formulaire de contact</div>
          <h2 class="h1" style="margin-top:16px;">Pour ce qui peut<br/>attendre 24 h.</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="lead section-head__lead">Questions, suggestions, partenariats, retours d'expérience. <strong>Pour une commande, appelez plutôt</strong> : c'est instantané.</p>
      </div>

      <form class="contact-form" data-form="contact" novalidate data-reveal>
        <div class="contact-form__grid">
          <div class="field">
            <label for="c-name">Nom <span class="req">*</span></label>
            <input id="c-name" name="name" type="text" required placeholder="Votre nom" />
          </div>
          <div class="field">
            <label for="c-email">Courriel <span class="req">*</span></label>
            <input id="c-email" name="email" type="email" required placeholder="vous@exemple.ca" />
          </div>
          <div class="field">
            <label for="c-phone">Téléphone</label>
            <input id="c-phone" name="phone" type="tel" data-phone placeholder="(873) 200-7377" />
          </div>
          <div class="field">
            <label for="c-subject">Sujet <span class="req">*</span></label>
            <select id="c-subject" name="subject" required>
              <option value="">Choisir…</option>
              <option>Question générale</option>
              <option>Partenariat / B2B</option>
              <option>Suggestion / commentaire</option>
              <option>Retour d'expérience</option>
              <option>Question sur la facturation</option>
              <option>Autre</option>
            </select>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="field">
          <label for="c-msg">Message <span class="req">*</span></label>
          <textarea id="c-msg" name="message" required rows="5" placeholder="Dites-nous ce qu'on peut faire pour vous."></textarea>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-form__submit">
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn--primary btn--xl">
            Envoyer le message
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </button>
          <span class="mono muted">Réponse sous 24 h ouvrables · pour une commande, appelez</span>
        </div>
        <div class="form-status" data-form-status></div>
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ========== BIG CTA ========== -->
  <section class="bigcta">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="bigcta__box">
        <div>
          <div class="kicker" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);">Une dernière fois</div>
          <h2 class="h-display" style="color:#fff;margin-top:16px;font-size:clamp(40px,8vw,96px);">
            Le numéro,<br/>encore une fois.
          </h2>
          <p class="lead" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.78);max-width:48ch;margin-top:20px;">Sept jours sur sept. Réponse rapide. Tarif annoncé d'avance.</p>
          <div style="display:flex;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:32px;">
            <a class="btn btn--primary btn--xl" href="tel:+18732007377" style="background:#fff;color:var(--blue-700);">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72c.13.96.36 1.9.7 2.81a2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45c.91.34 1.85.57 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/></svg>
              873 200-7377
            </a>
            <a class="btn btn--xl" style="background:transparent;color:#fff;border-color:rgba(255,255,255,.3);" href="/#commander">Commander en ligne</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bigcta__side mono">
          <div><span>BASE</span><strong>8 $</strong></div>
          <div><span>PAR KM</span><strong>+1 $</strong></div>
          <div><span>RAYON</span><strong>0–9 KM</strong></div>
          <div><span>OUVERT</span><strong>7 J/7</strong></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
